data.title: Boston Celtics Roster, Schedule, Stats (2006-2007)

data.text:
2006-2007 - Points

Paul Pierce scores a season high 39 points for Boston Celtics

On November 11, 2006, Paul Pierce set a season high in points in a NBA game. That day he scored 39 points in Boston Celtics's road win against New York Knicks, 118-122. He also had 9 rebounds, 4 assists, 2 steals and finished the game with a 37 efficiency.

2006-2007 - Rebounds

Al Jefferson grabs a season high 22 rebounds for Boston Celtics

On January 01, 2007, Al Jefferson set a season high in rebounds in a NBA game. That day he grabbed 22 rebounds in Boston Celtics's road loss against Detroit Pistons, 81-73. He also had 12 points, 1 assist and finished the game with a 22 efficiency.

2006-2007 - Assists

Rajon Rondo dishes a season high 11 assists for Boston Celtics

On February 02, 2007, Rajon Rondo set a season high in assists in a NBA game. That day he dished 11 assists in Boston Celtics's road loss against Detroit Pistons, 109-102. He also had 8 points, 2 rebounds, 1 steal and finished the game with a 16 efficiency.

2006-2007 - Steals

Tony Allen has a season high 7 steals for Boston Celtics

On January 01, 2007, Tony Allen set a season high in steals in a NBA game. That day he reached 7 steals in Boston Celtics's road loss against Orlando Magic, 87-79. He also had 21 points, 9 rebounds, 7 steals and finished the game with a 28 efficiency.

2006-2007 - Blocks

Al Jefferson blocks a season high 5 blocks for Boston Celtics Al Jefferson

On February 02, 2007, Al Jefferson set a season high in blocks in a NBA game. That day he went for 5 blocks in Boston Celtics's road loss against Utah Jazz, 105-87. He also had 12 points, 13 rebounds, 1 steal and finished the game with a 21 efficiency.

2006-2007 - Efficiency

Al Jefferson set a season high 44 efficiency for Boston Celtics

On March 03, 2007, Al Jefferson set a season high in efficiency in a NBA game. That day he accomplished 44 efficiency in Boston Celtics's home win against Seattle Sonics, 118-103. He also had 31 points, 16 rebounds, 1 steal and finished the game with a 44 efficiency.
